Happiest when enjoying a simple life with six square meals a day, Hobbits are solid and dependable when called to action. Playable classes:
  • Minstrel
  • Guardian
  • Hunter
  • Burglar

Not as long-lived as Elves, sturdy as Dwarves, or resilient as Hobbits, Men are renowned for their courage and resourcefulness. Playable classes:
  • Minstrel
  • Captain
  • Guardian
  • Hunter
  • Lore-master
  • Burglar
  • Champion

Long ago, the Elves welcomed the younger races of Middle-earth and allied with them when the need was great, but centuries of war, betrayal, and hardship have made them fiercely protective of their seclusion. Playable classes:
  • Minstrel
  • Guardian
  • Hunter
  • Lore-master
  • Champion

Dwellers of stone and miners of metal, the Dwarves are a doughty folk, resistant to the corruption of the Enemy -- but not to greed. Playable classes:
  • Minstrel
  • Guardian
  • Hunter
  • Champion
